formula: a(n) = (1/n)*(Sum_{d|n} mu(n/d)*binomial(5*d, d)) - 4*binomial(5*n, n)/(4*n+1) for n > 0. - _Andrew Howroyd_, May 02 2018
mathematica: a[n_] := DivisorSum[n, MoebiusMu[n/#] Binomial[5#, #]&]/n - 4 Binomial[5n, n]/(4n+1);
